The paper deals with trajectory planning and coordination of multiple mobile robots, which is a core problem in the field of robotics. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes revised and decentralized versions of prioritized planning algorithms, which involve artificial intelligence and distributed computing, respectively, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) likely sub-categories as well. The paper also deals with system-level control and coordination, which falls under the scope of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), respectively, making them likely sub-categories too.
